        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-blue-400">üîê Passwordless Auth</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300">
          WebAuthn (Passkeys) for secure, phishing-resistant authentication without passwords.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-purple-400">üåê OIDC Provider</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300">
          Full OpenID Connect compliance for single sign-on with modern applications.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-green-400">‚ö° Edge Native</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300">
          Built on Cloudflare Workers, D1, KV, and Durable Objects for global low-latency performance.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-yellow-400">üõ°Ô∏è Secure by Default</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300">
          HttpOnly cookies, CORS protection, CSP headers, and rate limiting included.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-8 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">Try It Out</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href="/login"
          class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-medium py-3 px-6 rounded-lg transition text-center"
        >
          Sign In with Passkey
        </a>
        <a
          href="/profile"
          class="bg-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-600 text-white font-medium py-3 px-6 rounded-lg transition text-center"
        >
          View Profile
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-gray-800/50 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-300">Project Status</h2>
      <div class="space-y-2 text-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center">
          <span class="text-green-400 mr-2">‚úÖ</span>
